description.en:
NADA Protocol Token is a Hedera-based reward-type token commonly used in an ecosystem where blockchain-based NFT mobile games and metaverses.
NADA Protocol Token is organically connected, developed, and supplied by NADA digital Co., Ltd., one of Korea's top 100 game developers.
